That's a good point. I will need to ask MVD what the new rules are here in
AZ. Now in AZ when you sell a vehicle you are supposed to remove the plate
and turn it in or move it to the new vehicle. If you turn them in you get a
refund on the spot of unused registration fees. Got back 18 bucks when I
turned some plates in last month!!

ronnie

